column6: "CAPTAIN AMERICA LIVES AGAIN" pt. 3 (of 4) Captain America (with assistance from the FF, the Avengers, the Punisher, Daredevil, and many other classic Marvel characters) fights the world-domineering Nazis in a strange new reality. Can Cap set the world right again?! 32 PGS./MARVEL PSR...$2.99
